title: LibriVox Short Nonfiction Collection Vol. 029
creator: Various
source: Librivox recording of a public-domain text
description: LibriVox recording of Short Nonfiction Collection Vol. 029 by Various Authors Read by LibriVox Volunteers Twenty short nonfiction works in the public domain, independently chosen by the readers. Topics include architecture, education, philosophy, religion, health, humor, history, and literature. (Summary by Sue Anderson) For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording. For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org. Download M4B (160mb)
